examples.en: She has a good figure.

examples.en: I figured that you wanted me to stay.

examples.en: I was never much good at figures.

examples.en: You can't figure on the results of the election.

examples.en: It figures: when I have the time to travel, I don't have the money.

examples.en: Michelangelo was one of the greatest figures of the Renaissance.

examples.en: I always figure on succeeding.

examples.en: I figure it must be close to three miles.

examples.en: Are you sure of your figures?
examples.ru: Ты уверен в своих расчётах?

examples.en: Can you figure out how to do it?

examples.en: We figured that we would arrive at around two o'clock.
examples.ru: Мы подсчитали, что приедем около двух часов.

examples.en: It was worth the trouble, I figured.

examples.en: Father is trying to figure out his tax.

examples.en: The wallpaper was figured with rosebuds.

examples.en: Unemployment is way above the official figure.
examples.ru: Безработица намного превышает официальные цифры.

examples.en: She has a trim figure.
